# Legacy Fig autocomplete clone. The importer that consumed this
# (scripts/import-fig-specs.mjs) was retired after Fig was sunset by
# Amazon in Sep 2024. bundle.json is now the source of truth. This
# directory may linger on older dev machines from earlier imports —
# ignore it defensively so `git add .` doesn't pull in ~50 MB of
# abandoned upstream TypeScript. Safe to delete locally any time.
.fig-autocomplete-source/

